Updated Syllabus (1st part) (2/2)
Linear classifiers and non-linear classifiers:
The perceptron algorithm and LSE for optimal linear classifiers;
Analysis of the XOR problem and the Multi-Layer Perceptron (MLP);
Training of MLPs and the Radial Basis Function Networks (RBF).
Linear Regression and Non-parametric PR methods:
LSE for linear regression, the ridge regression and Lasso regression;
Classification And Regression Trees (CART);
Bootstrap aggregating and Random Forests (RF).
